Version 0.3.1
=============

* Crudely update to work with LLVM 3.7, as 3.3 is creakingly old.
* Some C++11isms, sorry. It really needs a proper conversion pass.

Version 0.3
===========

(changelog lost)

Version 0.2
===========

* n-vector support.
* method calls can have parameters.
* type inference on variable declarations.
* global variables in the symbol table.
* better registration of external functions.
* Add pi, Inf, NaN constants.
* Added test suite.
* Many bugfixes and improves to demo code.

Version 0.1
===========

Initial version.
